        Parameters:
        broker - TradingBroker broker.
        strategy - TradingStrategy strategy.
        coinName - String name of the coin.
        action - String either a "Buy" or "Sell" action.
        quantity - int amount of coins traded.
        price - double the price at which the coin was traded at.
